@page
 
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "About MoneroMarketCap — a cryptocurrency market cap and price tracker that values every coin in Monero (XMR), built for people who think in Monero first.";
}

<h2>About MoneroMarketCap</h2>

<p>
    MoneroMarketCap tracks Monero (XMR) alongside the wider cryptocurrency
    market, with prices and market caps that can be valued directly in XMR.
    It's built for people who think in Monero first and want a clean,
    privacy-respecting way to follow the market.
</p>

<p>
    MoneroMarketCap is a project from
    <a href="https://monerica.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Monerica</a>,
    a curated directory of Monero-accepting merchants, services, and resources.
    It's part of a small family of Monerica tools built around the Monero
    ecosystem, and like the rest of the project it's open source — the full
    source code is available on
    <a href="https://github.com/monerica-project/MoneroMarketCap" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
</p>

<p>
    Market and price data is provided by the
    <a href="https://www.coingecko.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CoinGecko</a>
    API. Monero's own supply figures may additionally be verified against a
    self-hosted Monero node where available. Data is cached and refreshed
    periodically, so values can lag the live market by a few minutes.
</p>

<p>
    Exchange data is provided through a partnership with
    <a href="https://swapraven.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SwapRaven</a>,
    a vetted directory of no-KYC crypto swap exchanges. Each coin page lists the
    exchanges that support that coin — with SwapRaven's grade, KYC and AML posture,
    and fees — linking through to the full profile on SwapRaven.
</p>

<p style="color:var(--xmr-text-muted);font-size:0.85rem">
    Powered by CoinGecko. MoneroMarketCap is provided for informational
    purposes only and is not financial advice.
</p>